Pimco Sees China’s Growth Outlook Lower Than Consensus, Inflation Higher

-- B y   C a n d i c e   Z a c h a r i a h s
-- 
2011-05-02T00:05:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/pimco-sees-china-s-growth-outlook-lower-than-consensus-inflation-higher.html
Pacific Investment Management Co.,
which runs the world’s largest bond fund, said it expects
 China ’s economy to grow at a slower pace than consensus
forecasts while inflation is likely to be quicker than many are
predicting.  The South Korean won and China’s yuan are likely to advance
and  Japan ’s yen may decline, the  Newport Beach , California-based
company said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Candice Zachariahs in Sydney at 
